{"tid":1472282,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"不要說「回應訴求」，試著說「答應要求」。","createTime":"2019-08-14T13:50:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T13:57:19.000Z","uid":53687,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f33d92c8872720fa67066368ca8f91b504f61e1f","tid":1472282,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:50:37.000Z","msg":"一直覺得「回應訴求」呢個講法好奇怪，<br />\n「回應」本身係中性，無論答YES定NO都係回應嘅一種，<br />\n所以林鄭可以話已經回應咗你，就係SAY NO，而家我哋要佢SAY YES，所以應用「答應」。<br />\n「訴求」本身太過卑躬屈膝，而家民意好明顯，政府順民意答應係應份，所以應該用「要求」，<br />\n所以以後請講‧「答應五大要求」。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12c5a551edda11fbaf5adfa92403d2d3f8136df6","tid":1472282,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:50:57.000Z","msg":"答應要求！"},{"pid":"14b8c55c1cbbeba637fee7860589a45c4c675e35","tid":1472282,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:57:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}